Teller --|> Staff

' Customer Service Officer extends Staff
CSO --|> Staff
CSO --> UC7
CSO --> UC11
CSO --> UC13
CSO --> UC21
CSO --> UC24

' Supervisor extends Staff
Supervisor --|> Staff
Supervisor --> UC22
Supervisor --> UC23
Supervisor --> UC25
Supervisor --> UC26
Supervisor --> UC27
Supervisor --> UC28
Supervisor --> UC29
Supervisor --> UC31
Supervisor --> UC32

' Admin extends Supervisor
Admin --|> Supervisor
Admin --> UC3
Admin --> UC33

